          "id": "medmcqa-8ae919dd-e996-4d5e-a221-e70c6f65631e",
          "text": "Part of eukaryotic DNA contributing to polypetide synthesisa) Exonb) Enhancerc) Leader sequenced) tRNAe) ncRNA",
