          "id": "medmcqa-c4675e2f-981c-4d12-831f-2b2e961f1e4f",
          "text": "A 30-year-old male has had multiple episodes of sudden, severe pain, redness, and swelling of metatarsophalangeal joint of his great toes. These problems seem to occur after the man has had a night out on the town with his friends, when they go barhopping, and the night usually ends with a cab ride home for the group. This problem would also be exacerbated if the man eats which one of the following during his night out?",
